Nollywood actress Omotola Jalade-Ekeinde has taken to her social media page to celebrate her husband, Capt. Matthew Ekeinde on their 25th wedding anniversary. The super-talented personality and mother of four, who recently had her name trademarked, penned down a brief yet weighty message to mark their silver jubilee in marriage. She also posted a fascinating picture to that effect captioned: “25 Years Strong! Happy Marriage Anniversary to us.” Meanwhile, she has also posted lovely pictures to celebrate her husband’s 53rd birthday, which obviously coincides with their anniversary. The award-winning actress wrote: “Happy birthday to a Rare kind of Man. “You need to be studied. “YOUR Type is probably One in a Century. “Live Long King! “Love you forever My Captain.”